div.page
  div.col-md-6(data-ng-class="{'col-md-12': !vm.details}")
    div.panel
      p
        | The delete user and user index api routes are restricted to users with the 'admin' role.
      ul.list-group
        li.list-group-item(ng-repeat='user in vm.users')

          strong {{user.name}}
          button.btn.btn-primary.pull-right(ng-click="vm.showUser(user);")
            i.fa.fa-chevron-left(data-ng-show="vm.details")
            i.fa.fa-chevron-right(data-ng-hide="vm.details")
          br
          span.text-muted {{user.email}}
          //- a.trash(ng-click='vm.remove(user)')
          //-   span.glyphicon.glyphicon-trash.pull-right

  div.col-md-6(data-ng-show="vm.details")
    div.panel
      {{vm.currentUser}}
